data.description: Move Right In! Many updates to this lovely 4 bedroom home. Enjoy the beautiful kitchen with stainless appliances, newer cabinets, flooring and countertops. Get ready to entertain! The dining area has French doors that lead to a newer patio and privacy fenced back yard. Bathroom has newer tile, lighting and fixtures. Two main floor bedrooms and two bedrooms upstairs. Roof replaced 2018. Siding 2017. Don't miss this one!
